This folder contains all of the systems tools and utilities which is offered to the user.
Theses tools enable the user to perform several useful tasks.

Included:

>Email system
>Create recipe forms
>show wastage graph form
>shopping list form
>Nutrition List form
>Hourglass form (a timer in form of a progress bar indicating expiry progress)
>manage budget form - calculates maximum spending budget for a duration
>login forms
>registry forms
>user forms
